Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward ray stokes FBI\NEdward ray stokes, fbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放下枪\NDrop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们先放下\NYou first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们收到了你的信 edward\NWe got your letters, edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,读了每一个字\NI read every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你明白了\NThen you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我明白你的愤怒\NYeah, I understand that you're angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你心灵受到创伤\NAnd you hurt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但那个女孩 她叫sheryl\NBut that girl, her name is sheryl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是你母亲\NAnd she is not your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有像你母亲一样伤害你\NShe didn't hurt you like your mother did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她必须死\NShe needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是今天\NNo. Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放下枪 edward\NPut it down, edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Blake 你还好吗\NBlake. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要医生\NWe need a medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  我还好  没事\NI'm all right. I'm ok. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 hotch 机场见\NUh-huh. You got it, hotch. We'll meet you at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定没事\NYou sure you're ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 没有什么\NOh, yeah. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,离要害就几英寸\NA couple inches to your right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他本可以射击你的臂动脉\Nand he could have hit your brachial artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 你相当幸运啊\NAll things considered, you were extraordinarily lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,与运气无关\NYeah, luck had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我刀枪不入\NI'm practically bulletproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过\NYeah, I heard that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  快点完事回家吧\NAll right, let's finish this up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸\NHey, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\NYeah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NHow are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 我们才完事\NNo, no, we're just finishing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我们其实在\NNo, we're actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光充足的洛杉矶\NUh, in sunny los angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 一切还好吗\NWhy? Everything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,帮什么忙\NHelp with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 长官 我准备好了\NOk, sir, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 大家注意一下\NAll right. Can I have your attention, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧 garcia\NGo ahead, garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 昨晚在堪萨斯城\NAlrighty, then. Last night in kansas city--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,严格地说是今天清晨\NWell, technically super early this morning--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,50岁的david morrison\N50-year-old david morrison
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,慢跑时被打死了\Nwas beaten to death when he was out jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,信息显示在你们的平板上\NInformation is on your tablets right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真残忍\NIt looks brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,典型的暴力杀害\NClassic overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他被剥光  穿着女人的内衣\NHe was found stripped and wearing women's underwear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想内衣应该不是他的\NThat I'm assuming weren't his.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 附近发现了他所有的衣物\NYeah. All of his clothes were found nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,包括内衣\Nhis skivvies included.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有性侵犯的迹象吗\NAny evidence of sexual assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在等报告结果\NWe're still waiting on the m.E. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有其他受害者吗 garcia\NAny other victims, garcia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大有可能\NThat is a big maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看看tommy barnes和melissa hawthorne\NMeet tommy barnes and melissa hawthorne,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也显示在你们的平板上\NAlso on your tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一年前 他们在家庭派对上消失\NA year ago they disappeared from a house party
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被发现以相同的手法暴打致死\NAnd were found beaten in much the same fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个人 他们明显\NThere were two of them and they're considerably younger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比最近的受害者年轻\NThan this most recent victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,女人的内衣呢\NYeah, and what about the women's underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是一种特定仪式\NAnd that's a pretty specific ritual aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个都穿着衣服\NThese two were found fully clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确定是同一嫌犯所为吗\NAre we sure that it's the same unsub?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我老爸这样认为\NMy dad thinks it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸是堪萨斯城的城市警察 对吧\NYour dad's a captain on the kansas city police force, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,退休了\NRetired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但你哥哥也是警察\NBut your brother's a cop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Scott 他是罪案侦探\NScott. He's a homicide detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但打电话的是我爸\NBut my dad is the one who made the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他退休了 这未必就是官方邀请\NIf he's retired, it's not exactly an official invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但他很有影响力\NNo, but he's got lots of influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该等候邀请\NWell, maybe we should wait for the invite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能强行介入当地管辖范围\NWe can't just force ourselves on local jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是连杀案呢\NWhat if it's actually serial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们要求 我们就回去\NWe'll go back if they ask us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我爸是一个伟大的警察 他几乎没犯过错\NLook, my dad's a great cop, and he's almost never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我快疯了 但那是真的\NI mean, it drives me crazy, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不确定到底得到了什么线索\NWe don't know exactly what we've got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但我认为值得看一下\NBut I think it's worth taking a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让飞行员返航去堪萨斯城\NHave the pilot reroute us to kansas city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹亲如手足\N"Brothers and sisters are as close as hands and feet."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,越南谚语\NVietnamese proverb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,David morrison是一名小说家\NDavid morrison was a novelist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy barnes和melissa hawthorne是高中生\NTommy barnes and melissa hawthorne high school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,受害人之间没有明显联系\NNo apparent connection between the victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,DNA采样不匹配\NNo matching dna samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,被害相隔整整一年\NAnd an entire year between kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,内衣仪式或许是关于象征性的羞辱\NYou know, the underwear ritual may be about symbolic humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是给发现者的冲击\NOr a shock factor for whoever found the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Blake 你爸爸有提到其他的原因吗\NBlake, did your dad say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他认为这些案件是有关联的\Nelse about why he thinks these cases are connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Blake\NYeah? Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗\NEverything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 抱歉\NUh, yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点分心\NJust--I'm distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以理解 熟悉的声音 场景\NPerfectly understandable. The familiar sounds, visual cues,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至味道 会触发记忆与情感\NEven olfactory inputs, can trigger memories and emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那些以为离我们远去的东西\NWe thought were long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我回家也这样\NHappens to me every time I go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,上次回家是什么时候\NWhen was the last time you were back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,422天前\NIt's been like 422 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我在问blake\NI was talking to blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多5年了\NUh, it's been about 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很久了\NThat's a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一走出堪萨斯城\NYeah, once I got out of kansas city,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我就很想呆在外面\NI pretty much wanted to stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她最大的哥哥持械抢劫\NHer oldest brother was responding to an armed robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,显然坏家伙都喜欢毒品\NApparently the bad guys were on pcp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他和他的伙伴中枪 他最严重\NBoth he and his partner got shot and he got the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么对此一无所知\NHow come we don't know any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她该说什么\NWhat's she supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,随便说点什么\NSomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,blake是个安静的人\NWell, blake's a private person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她不想和她的家人交流\NMaybe she doesn't want to talk about her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而且已经过去25年 过去很久了\NPlus it was over 25 years ago. A lot of time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这样失去我父亲的\NI lost my father the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是我不想联系\NIt's not like I can't relate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你很少谈论他\NYeah, but you rarely talk about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有自己的悲伤\NEverybody grieves in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能对她发怒\NYou can't be mad at her for going internal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有 我只是\NOh, I'm not mad at all. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得她该说点什么\NThought she might say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事上 你帮不了忙\NThere's nothing for you to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸预感此事时 你就应该知道\NWhen dad has a hunch, you know how he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 他直接打电话给garrity队长\NYeah, he called captain garrity directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\NSo, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,队长希望我配合 就这样\NWell, the captain wants me to cooperate, that's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是在浪费时间\NBut you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸似乎不这样看\NDad doesn't seem to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子和morrison谋杀无关 好吗\NLook, those kids had nothing to do with the morrison murder, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们被杀害在prospect被杀害\NThey were killed down on prospect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们不过也就抓了一些小人物\NBecause they were out trying to cop some weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prospect\NProspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prospect大道 一个犯罪高发区\NUh, prospect avenue. It's a high crime area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们这个地方\NIt's the hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,miller警探 我向你保证\NDetective miller, I assure you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是到这里侵权的\NWe're not here to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我确信在未来的24小时也不会\NAnd I feel certain that in 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以调查出这些案件是否相关\NWe'll be able to discern whether these cases are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的做的很好 Scoot\NWe're really good at what we do, scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是当然\NOf course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex?\NAlex?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\NDad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦...已经这么久了\NOh...been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来不错 抱歉我有点迟到\NYou look good. I'm sorry I'm a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才在garrity的办公室耽搁了一会\NI was down in garrity's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是hotchner\NYou must be hotchner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damon miller 是的 先生\NDamon miller. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\NVery nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来\NAppreciate you coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢这么照顾我女儿\NAnd thanks for taking such good care of my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,关于案子有什么计划?\NSo what's the plan of attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很偏僻\NThis place is pretty isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,使用棍子很方便\NIt helps to be out in the sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要打死一个人\NIf you're going to beat someone to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来你很有经验\NYou sound like you speak from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,David morrison是个50岁的小说家\NDavid morrison was a 50-year-old novelist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,显然还是个多才多艺的三项全能运动员\NAnd apparently an accomplished triathlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,埋伏的好地方\NGood place for an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要选这样一个人\NBut why pick the in-shape guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Morrison也许就是目标\NMorrison could have been a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他认识凶手\NMaybe he knew his killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可能有什么过节\NBut they may have had some kind of a beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,打死一个人是个人行为\NBeating someone to death is personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是有很强的愤怒\NIt takes a lot of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人一定是身体很强健\NWell, the unsub's got to be physically fit himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对 还有很高等级的暴力倾向\NYeah, he would have to be to maintain that level of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他也有可能是个瘾君子\NHe could also be on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的假设\NThat's a good bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像是毁灭性的攻击\NAll right, so, it looks like it's a blitz attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他怎么做到的\NHow do you think he did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手跟踪morrison\NWell, the unsub stalks morrison
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,调查他的生活\NAnd figures out that this is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道他在哪晨跑\NWhere he takes his morning run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他等待 藏起来\NThen he waits, hides,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,冲向他\NJumps him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他跟踪他来这\NOr he follows him out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把他制服 虽然morrison是三项全能\NRuns him down, even though morrison is a triathlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望这凶手没有别的目标了\NWell, I just hope this guy doesn't have any more targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是愤怒或者是成瘾了\NIf this is rage and addiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那他还没完\NHe's not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说\NI'm just saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以打给我的 爸爸\NYou could have called me, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,直接去找我上司\NGoing straight to my boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有她\NOh, and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这会让我看起来怎样?\NI mean, how do you think this makes me look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为什么 因为你的直觉\NBecause why? Because you have a hunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果我打电话你会说什么?\NAnd what would you have said if I'd called?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会...\NI'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,恩-恩\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她不像是伸手要什么\NAnd it's not like she would ever reach out and offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经有五年没有在家了\NShe hasn't been home in 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该飞去washington看她\NI had to fly out to washington just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这\NI'm right here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我只是想说\NLook, all I'm saying, dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个部门其实\NIs the last thing this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,无非需要的只是这样一个消息\Ndepartment needs is some bad press that comes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是FBI到这来抓连环杀手\NFrom an fbi serial killer hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这个部门最需要的\NThe last thing this department needs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是将这个连环杀手伏法\NIs a serial killer on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她说得没错\NShe's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也知道\NAnd you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道么 爸爸\NYou know what, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 来啊 来啊 说出来\NWhat?! Come on, come on, speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你退休了\NHey. You're retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他退休了\NHe's--he's retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好么 为什么你还一直坚持\NOk? And why are you sticking your nose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一件和你无关的事情\NWhere it doesn't belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是你爸\NBecause I am your father
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想坚持我就坚持\NAnd I will stick my nose wherever I damn well please
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我死了 而且就我的年纪来看\NUntil the day I die, and given my age,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天也不远了\NThat day ain't too far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 我老了 爸\NWhat? I'm old. Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我跟你做个交易\NBut I'll make you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始你们得表现的亲密一点\NYou two both start acting like you're related
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了\NAnd I'll butt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到这个凶手的唯一方法\NThe only way you're gonna catch this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你们团结起来\NIs if you do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没 只是点咖啡因\NNo, just a little caffeine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 他的兴奋剂检测结果是阴性\NOther than that, his tox screen was negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他脖子周围有非常重的淤青\NThat pretty heavy bruising around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,死因是窒息\NYeah. Cause of death was asphyxiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这里奇怪的颈椎骨折了么?\NAnd you see this odd little cervical fracture right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来他是被什么闷住的\NIt looks like he got put in some kind of choke hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,闷死一个人是很困难的\NChoking someone out is hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在做这事的时候弄断他们的脖子\NBut to break their neck while you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 他是个该死的壮汉\NYeah, well, he was a strong son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,四根肋骨断了 左臂粉碎\N4 ribs were broken, radius in his left arm was shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,颅骨线形骨折 下巴破裂\NLinear fracture in his skull, broken jaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,脾脏破裂\NAnd a ruptured spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我他可能用了什么武器么\NCan you tell if he used a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他没用什么武器 看到这的淤青了么\NI don't think he did. See this bruising right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他就是用他的手而已\NIt looks like he used his bare hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是他的靴子\NMaybe his boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他被闷死的相当迅速\NBut he was suffocated fairly quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分这些都是死后造成的\NMost of this is postmortem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙一定在经历什么\NThis guy had to be on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说?\NWhy do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他疯了\NBecause he went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是愤怒了\NThis is more than just rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有性侵犯的迹象吗\NWas there any evidence of sexual assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这和tommy barnes或者melissa hawthorne看起来都不一样\NIt wasn't like this with tommy barnes or melissa hawthorne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个被杀的高中生\NThose two high school kids who were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,报告里说他们没有任何死后造成的伤痕\NThe report says that they didn't have any postmortem wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是同一个凶手?\NGod, you think it's the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还得这样来一次么\NDo we have to go through this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不是都写到报告里了么\NIsn't it all in your report?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 Barnes先生\NI apologize, mr. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是很难的\NI know this is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想更彻底一点\NWe're just trying to be thorough
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那样我们才能抓到杀害你儿子的凶手\NSo we can catch whoever did this to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的回答和一年前他们问我的都是一样的\NAll my answers are the same they were a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是因为是你发现tommy 和 melissa的\NBut since you were the one that actually found tommy and melissa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这点尤其重要\NIt's especially important
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们还要再来一遍\NThat we go through it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NOk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在跟我讲讲那个晚上\NYou were telling me about that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很晚了 你开始担心了\NIt was late and you were getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我记得tommy\NAnd then I remembered that tommy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在我手机里加了一个"找朋友"的软件\NPut that "Find your friends" App on my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,几个小时以后\NAnd a couple hours later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在山谷中发现了他和Melissa\NI found him and melissa in the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy有死敌吗\NDid tommy have any enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会伤害他的人\NSomeone that might want to hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他是个好孩子  我已经说过了\NNo, he was a good kid. I said that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  听着\NAll right, listen. We
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你能过来   Barnes先生\Nwant to thank you for coming in, mr. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\NWe appreciate it. If we have
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果其他问题   我们再给你打电话\Nany other questions, we'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  你能在等会吗\NActually...will you give us a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有几个问题  不会太久的\NI just have a few more questions. Won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Scott\NScott.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NExcuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他在竭力隐瞒什么东西\NHe's holding something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是为失去儿子而悲伤\NHe's grieving the loss of his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  从他坐下的那一刻\NExactly. And he's been trying to get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他就一直想离开这里\NEver since he sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你能怪他吗\NCan you blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我自己的孩子被杀害了\NIf I had a kid who was killed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI想帮我找出凶手的话\NAnd the fbi wanted to help find the guy who did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意配合他们做任何事\NI would do whatever they asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他的神态\NLook at his posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,焦躁不安\NHe's too agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的话很可疑  我不能\NThere is something odd about his syntax I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也说不上来是什么\NThat I can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢   因为这个案件对我来说太复杂了吗\NAnd why is that? Because that profile's too complicated for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是这样吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗\NRight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  Scott\NPlease, scott,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次\NFor once,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,按我说的办吧\NJust go with me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Barnes先生  很抱歉要问你这个问题\NMr. Barnes, I am so sorry to have to ask you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想浪费你的时间\NBut I don't want to waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的一切都是为了抓住凶手\NAll I want to do is catch the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有你的配合  我是抓不到的\NBut I can't do that unless you're straight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex\NAlex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当你找到Tommy和Melissa的时候\NWhen you found tommy and melissa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们穿衣服了没\NWere they clothed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你什么意思\NI don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  Tommy是不是穿着女孩的内衣呢\NI mean, was tommy in girls underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要尊重你儿子的回忆\NIf you want to honor your son's memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,或者给其他受害者的亲人一点安慰\NMaybe bring some peace to the relatives of the other victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托了\NThen, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托告诉我真相吧\NJust tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  不能\NI couldn't--I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没事的  我们是要帮你\NNo, it's all right. We only want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当我找到他们时\NWhen I found them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她没穿衣服  而Tom\NShe was naked, and tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy穿着女孩的内裤\NTommy, he was in girls panties,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\NAnd I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让他们看见他穿成这样  所以\NCouldn't let them see him like that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就给他脱了下来\NI took them off and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,穿在了Melissa的身上  我\NI put them on melissa and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他们都把衣服穿好了  抱歉\NI put all their clothes back on. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没事的\NNo, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\NWe ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就等你了  亲爱的\NJust waiting on you, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你把Rufus放出去了吗\NDid you let rufus out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为是你放出去的\NI thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NTsk. Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rufus\NRufus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rufus\NOh, rufus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧\NEverything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  是这只笨猫\NYeah. This dumb cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gil和Renee Patterson都是勤劳善良的人\NGil and renee patterson were good, hard-working people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他是银行经理  而她是个护士\NHe was a bank manager, she was a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果目标是这些受害者的话  这其中有什么关联呢\NIf all these victims were targets, then what's the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也许目标不在他们  他们只是替罪羊\NMaybe they're not targets. Maybe they're surrogates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,替谁呢\NFor who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显  一个邻居在路过时看到门虚掩着\NSo, um, apparently, a neighbor found the bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后发现了尸体\NWhen she came by and saw the door was ajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Patterson夫妇有近亲吗\NDo the pattersons have any next of kin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要和他们谈谈\NWe're gonna need to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  有一个女儿叫做laurie\NYeah, they do. They have a daughter named laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是密苏里州大学的大四学生\NShe's a senior at the university of missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,惯用手法\NM.O.'s THE EXACT SAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,女人的内衣  人为的过度暴力伤害\NWomen's underwear, violent manual overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,显然是同一个人\NIt's definitely our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在变本加厉了\NAnd now he's accelerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,胆子也越来越大了\NAnd he's getting bolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前从未入过室\NHe's never broken into a home before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你发现什么了\NHey, what you got, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上死去的David Morrison\NSo it turns out our dead jogger david morrison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在出版第一本书之前\NBounced around as a substitute english teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,曾是名代课老师\NBefore he published his first book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,四年前  他曾在Jefferson高中工作过一个星期\N4 years ago, he worked for a week at jefferson high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那所学校正是\NAnd that is the same school
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy Barnes和Melissa Hawthorne曾上学的地方\NThat tommy barnes and melissa hawthorne went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Patterson夫妇有个女儿  Laurie\NLaurie. Jj: the pattersons have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Garcia  Laurie Patterson上哪个高中\NGarcia, where did laurie patterson go to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是在  Jefferson\NThat would be...jefferson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她是什么时候毕业的\NAnd when did she graduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,四年前\N4 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说她和Morrison同时在那上学\NSo she was there at the same time morrison was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我会给Hotch打电话  我们需要发文件\NAll right, I'll call hotch. We need to give the profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,基于受害者和当地人口统计\NBased on his victims and on local demographics,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以认定我们在找的是个毕加索男子\NWe believe we're looking for a caucasian male
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在他十几岁到二十几岁的时候\NIN HIS LATE TEENS TO EARLY 20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个虐待狂 有暴力倾向\NHe's a sadist with rage issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那就解释了\NWhich accounts for the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀害的五个受害者都是\NAll 5 of his victims are in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,和Jefferson高中有关的\Nsome way connected to jefferson high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这使我们有理由相信\NWhich leads us to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他要么曾是那的学生  要么是前雇员\Nhe's either a former student or employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是之前的\NWhy former?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们还认为他有染毒品\NBecause we also think he has a drug problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,毒瘾加上暴力问题\NThe addiction plus his anger issues
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说明他可能缺少社会技能\NMeans that he probably lacks the social skills
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,需要呆在学校  或者有一份稳定的工作\NRequired to stay in school or hold down a steady job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为暴力和虐待\NBecause brute force and humiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是他惯用手法的特点\NAre the hallmarks of his m.O.,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为他杀人是为了报复\NWe believe his kills are somehow rooted in revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能被虐待羞辱受过伤害\NWe think he may have been traumatically humiliated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在不久的过去\NIn some way in the recent past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是青少年时候\NProbably as an adolescent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他心中隐私的部分\NWhich makes this very personal to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那他为什么在第一次犯罪后隔了一整年呢\NSo why did this guy wait a whole year after his first murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为他可能被监禁过\NWe think he may have been incarcerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你应该看看暴力罪犯\NSo you should be looking at violent offenders
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,或者所有年轻点的你所熟悉的前科犯\NOr any younger ex-cons you may be familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为他的第一次谋杀是在做实验\NWe think his first kills were experiments of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是尝尝鲜\NHe was just getting a taste for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy Barnes和melissa Hawthorne\NTommy barnes and melissa hawthorne
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比其他的受害者受到的伤害都深\NHad more defensive wounds than any of his other victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,显然他们还做了好一番反抗\NAnd they apparently put up quite a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,同时袭击两个人可不是件易事\NIt's not easy to blitz attack two people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不论他是否被监禁了  他肯定用\NSo whether he was locked up or not, he probably took
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一年来完善自己\NA year off to perfect his
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,确保不再有意外发生\Ncraft to make sure that never happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他体型健康  也许经常锻炼\NHe's physically fit and probably works out a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他有可能常去不贵的体育馆或者健康俱乐部\NSo he may frequent inexpensive gyms or heath clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了  这家伙徒手\NAnd don't forget, this guy used his bare hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死了受害者\NTo kill his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会善罢甘休的\NHe will not be easily deterred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要谨慎行事\NSo proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,随着他越来越脱离现实\NAs his grip on reality continues to fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他会变得更危险\NHe'll become more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好你的东西  我们就要关门了\NHey, wrap it up, kid. We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  再来两轮\NFew more minutes. Two more rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚出去  我要关门走了\NHey, get the hell out. I gotta get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要几分钟\NI just need a few more minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NOk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你听清楚了没有\NAll right by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 没问题\NIt's all good, man. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想惹麻烦\NI don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该反复核对一下\NWe should cross-check our
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最近释放的前科犯的名单\Nlist of recently released ex-cons again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Garcia和我检查过两遍\NGarcia and I have been over it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有和资料相符合的人\NNobody matches the profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小妞  你难住我们整个团队了 说吧\NHey, baby girl, you got the whole crew. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  这是一个Jefferson高中的瘦小伙\NOk, here's the skinny on jefferson high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好球队  一连两次夺冠\NReally great football team, state champ two years in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  伙计们\NGo, bulldogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一值得注意的是那所高中\NThe only notable thing that has happened at that high school
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的10年中，除了\NIn the last 10 years besides the murder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommy Barnes 和Melissa Hawthorne的谋杀案\NOf tommy barnes and melissa hawthorne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个学生也遇害了\NIs the death of another student,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Riley wilson，死于4年前\NRiley wilson, 4 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,发送中\NSending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已将信息发至你的平板电脑\NInformation streaming to your tablets now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他在一根电线杆旁边把他的车裹起来\NHe wrapped his car around a telephone pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人猜测这是一起自杀事件\NYeah. There was a lot of speculation it was a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,报告里没有检出三聚甲醛\NTox report was clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他是完全清醒的\NHe was totally sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个高中生而且学习成绩一直优异\NHE WAS A SENIOR AND GOT STRAIGHT As.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有处分记录\NNothing in his disciplinary file.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他在Jefferson读高中时\NHe was at jefferson the same
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,David Morrison和Laurie Patterson也在同所学校\Ntime as david morrison and laurie patterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Garcia  我们需要Riley Wilson上学时\NGarcia, we need a list of every student and employee
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jefferson高中所有学生和员工的名单\NAt jefferson while riley wilson was a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,包括父母和家庭成员\NParents and family members, too, garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,列表正在筛选形成中\NCompiling that list now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,名字太多了  我会尽快给你回电。\NIt is a lot of names. I will hit you back asap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是以前的学生的部分名单\NHere's a partial list of former students
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是仍然住在城里的人\NWho still live in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么只有部分名单\NWhy partial?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经将范围缩小以便分工合作\NWe've narrowed it down so we can split the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会负责剩下的\NWe'll cover the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们继续努力吧\NOk. We'll get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其中一个人可能是不明嫌犯\NAnd, uh, one of those people may be the unsub,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那让你们那边的人注意一下\NSo, make sure your guys know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\NYou got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\NUh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是听我爸爸的\NI never would have shown up like I did
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根就不该出现的\NIf dad hadn't asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我理解你\NI mean, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你有权沮丧\NYou have every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex  没关系  好吧\NIt's all good, alex. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我好多年没见你了\NCome on. I haven't seen you in years
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们有这机会共事了\NAnd now we get this great chance to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我得开始工作去了\NI better get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Gates\NCharles gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Milller探员\NDetective miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,堪萨斯州警局\NKansas city police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我能否问你几个问题呢\NI was wondering if I could ask you a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:23:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NUm...sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我能进来吗\NMay I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NYeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  有点乱   没关系\NUm, sorry about the mess. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurie  我们你父母的事感到遗憾\NLaurie, we're so very sorry about your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来\NThank you for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道会发生这种事  难以承受\NWe know this-- this is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  我\NIt's ok, I, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还真不想回家\NDon't really want to go home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能帮你做点什么\NIs there anything we can get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在问你几个问题可以吗\NIs it ok if we ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.12,0:24:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想到有谁\NIs there anyone you know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可能伤害你父母的人吗\Nwho may have wanted to hurt your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那有没有人可能会伤害你\NIs there anyone who may have wanted to hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:24:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 我\NNo, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.37,0:24:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm--I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.01,0:24:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\NIt's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.11,0:24:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己待会  好吗\NWe're gonna give you a minute. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:24:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当我听说他死了的时候我真不敢相信\NI couldn't believe it when I heard he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.18,0:25:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  Riley连酒都不喝\NI mean, riley didn't even drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.99,0:25:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我前不久还见他呢\NAnd I'd just seen him at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.52,0:25:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你和他关系很好是吧\NSo you two were pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他不怎么喜欢社交\NI mean, he wasn't all that social.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.06,0:25:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,经常一个人独自呆着\NHe kept to himself a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.90,0:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他是那种独来独往的人\NSo he was kind of a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们经常翘课出去  我们很少一起上课\NBut we hung out. We had a few classes together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.94,0:25:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子\NLiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\NDad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.66,0:25:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他还好吧 发生什么事情了\NIs he ok? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.99,0:25:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他被打得挺严重的  特别是头部\NHe got beat up pretty bad. Took a blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.19,0:25:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他有搭档吗  他的伙伴在哪里\NDid he have backup? Where's his partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.40,0:26:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他一个人来的  为了混淆视听  他们是分头行动的\NHe came alone. They split up the list to cover more ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.60,0:26:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把他送到医院去\NLet's get him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.83,0:26:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我跟你一起去\NAll right, I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.03,0:26:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 你留在这 有更重要的事让你做\NNo, you stay here. You'll do more good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.80,0:26:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我会照顾好他的\NDon't worry. I'll-- I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.69,0:26:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯可能在你弟弟来之前就到了这里\NThe unsub was probably already here when your brother arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.90,0:26:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但没杀他\NBut he didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.03,0:26:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为Charles才是他的目标\NBecause charles was the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.57,0:26:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他弟弟只是诱饵\NSo this guy's mission oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.27,0:26:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为疑犯可能已经偷了scott的枪支。\NI believe the unsub may have stolen scott's firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.50,0:26:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不符合他的作案手法  但不代表他不用\NDoesn't match his m.O., but that won't stop him from using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.61,0:26:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有新发现\NThere's something in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.28,0:26:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他写道  Charles 和Riley是好朋友\NHe wrote, "Charles and riley good friends,"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.41,0:26:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在“好”和“朋友”下面划线强调了\NBut he underlined the words "Good" And "Friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.18,0:26:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说有何意义\NThat mean something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.52,0:26:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他小时候经常这么做\NYeah. He used to do that when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,通常被激怒了他才会这么做\NUsually when something really irritated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.22,0:26:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他在字下面划线是因为他愤怒了吗\NHe underlined words when he was irritated?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.29,0:27:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我母亲以前经常让我们互相写信\NYeah. Our mother used to make us write letters
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮助我们解决我们的冲突\NTo each other to help us resolve our conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.70,0:27:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她认为这是一种学习\NShe thought it was a good way to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.13,0:27:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,表达我们的感受的方式\NHow to express our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.47,0:27:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明的女士\NSmart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那好朋友的意思对他来说到底是关于什么呢\NWhat was it about the words "Good friends" That got to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.41,0:27:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  他怎么样\NHey, dad, how's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.58,0:27:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  laurie\NHi, laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.98,0:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗\NHow are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.75,0:27:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我还有些坏消息要告诉你\NI'm afraid I have some more bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.49,0:27:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手又行凶了\NThe killer struck again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.29,0:27:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是你以前的同学\NThis time it was a former classmate of yours--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.76,0:27:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles Gates\NCharles gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.96,0:27:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这对你来说是令人难以置信的痛苦\NI understand this is incredibly overwhelming,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.26,0:27:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们需要你的帮助\NBut we really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.57,0:27:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  我想问你一些事\NOk? I want to ask you about charles
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.50,0:27:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Charles和你老同学Riley Wilson\NAnd another former classmate of yours, riley wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.67,0:27:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有关他们的什么\NWhat about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.77,0:27:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是好朋友么\NWere they good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles和Riley么  不是\NCharles and riley? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.82,0:27:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Riley实际上没什么朋友\NRiley didn't really have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.19,0:28:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没有\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.29,0:28:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个纯种书呆子\NHe was a gigantic nerd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是个彻头彻尾的受害者\NAnd a total victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.30,0:28:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们过去经常欺负他\NThey used to bully him,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.90,0:28:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似一直那样\NLike all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.63,0:28:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都对他做过什么\NWhat would they do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.13,0:28:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,取笑他  揍他\NTease him. Beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.01,0:28:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  而且还有件内衣事件\NAnd then-- and then there was the underwear thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.04,0:28:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么内衣事件\NWhat underwear thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.71,0:28:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人觉得如果体育课上\NSome guys thought it'd be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.75,0:28:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,偷走Riley的衣服会很有意思\NIf they stole all riley's clothes in gym class.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.09,0:28:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  他出来了\NHey, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.33,0:28:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让他穿着一条女士短裤\NThey made him wear a pair of panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.53,0:28:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,并且给学校里的每个人发短信\NAnd then they sent out a mass text
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们在走廊里站成一排\NTo everyone in school telling them to line the hallways.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.67,0:28:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上全学校的学生都到了\NBasically the whole school showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.77,0:28:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个恶作剧是谁的主意\NWhose idea was it to pull the prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.31,0:29:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的前男友  Lance Tate\NMy ex-boyfriend, lance tate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个混蛋\NHe was a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,教师们当时在哪\NWhere were the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.63,0:29:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramsey先生和几个代课老师结束了这场闹剧\NMr. Ramsey and some substitute broke it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.33,0:29:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,各回各班吧\NGo back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都回去\NEverybody back to class!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,表演结束了\NShow's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.31,0:29:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他后来有没有出事\NDid anything happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.78,0:29:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lance惹上麻烦了么\NDid lance get in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.98,0:29:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.48,0:29:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他被欺负的孩子么\NWere there any other kids
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.77,0:29:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说Riley是唯一的一个\Nthat were bullied or was riley the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.12,0:29:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  还有其他人\NYeah, there were others.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.15,0:29:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得他们的名字么\NDo you remember their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.82,0:29:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等下  那个  那个和这有关么\NWait. Is that-- is that what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.89,0:29:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是为什么我父母被杀的原因吗\NIs that why my parents were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.19,0:29:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.43,0:29:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurie Patterson那时不在学校\NLaurie patterson was away at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.23,0:29:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他就不能跟踪她了\NSo he couldn't go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.67,0:29:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他转而跟踪了他的父母\NSo he goes after her parents instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.00,0:29:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是他使她的痛苦最大化的方法\NThat was his way of maximizing her suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.24,0:30:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurie的前男友  Lance Tate中士\NLaurie's ex, sergeant lance tate,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.34,0:30:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,第三次去阿富汗服役\NIs doing his third tour in afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.77,0:30:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的父母移居到了亚利桑那州\NHis parents moved to arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.14,0:30:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  在听你说话  Garcia\NHey. You're on speaker, garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.11,0:30:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚出炉的  我拿到了Laurie给我们的名单\NHot off my keyboard, I took the names laurie gave us
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.28,0:30:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们和Riley Wilson的短信\NAnd I cross-checked them with riley wilson's texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.52,0:30:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,电子邮件以及社交媒体交叉比对了  得到了2个匹配记录\NEmails, and social media. I got two hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.16,0:30:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是Kevin Russ  他的化学实验搭档\NOne's a kevin russ. That was his chemistry lab partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.06,0:30:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个也是更有意思的\NAnd the second and the way more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.03,0:30:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个叫做Ronald Underwood的孩子\NIs a kid named ronald underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.73,0:30:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他有什么有趣的\NWhat's so interesting about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.70,0:30:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似他们是很好的朋友\NIt looks like they were actually pretty good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.17,0:30:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ronald刚好是在Riley死后辍学的\NRonald dropped of school right after riley died.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.44,0:30:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Underwood我们还知道什么\NWhat else do we know about underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲不在  他和母亲一起生活\NUh, dad is out of the picture. He lives with his mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.14,0:30:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她有四次酒后驾车记录\NWHO HAS 4, 4 DUIs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.48,0:30:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在因特网上花费了难以想象的大把时间\NHe spends a cra-cra-crazy amount of time on the internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.55,0:30:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分是花在了浏览色情和综合搏击网站以及\NMostly looking at porn and mma sites and--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因特网也是他买到类固醇药物的地方\NOh. The internet is also where he buys his anabolic steroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.46,0:30:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这就是关于恃强凌弱的所有信息\NIf this is all about bullying,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.87,0:30:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么嫌疑犯本人可能也会成为受害人\Nthe unsub may have been a victim himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.86,0:30:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他也可能感到对Riley的死负有责任\NHe may also feel responsible for what happened to riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.76,0:30:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他将恃强者和没阻止Riley这场悲剧的\NAnd he's targeting the bullies
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.97,0:30:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,家长作为了报复目标\Nand the adults who did nothing to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.73,0:30:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurie说了恶作剧发生的那天\NLaurie said a substitute teacher and a mr. Ramsey
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一个代课老师和Ramsey先生在场\NWere there the day of the practical joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,David Morrison肯定是嫌疑犯\NDavid morrison had to be the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.37,0:31:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Garcia  Ramsey先生现在在哪\NGarcia, where's mr. Ramsey now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.17,0:31:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold Ramsey  历史教师\NHarold ramsey, history teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.31,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他在Jefferson高中工作\NLl works at jefferson high.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.74,0:31:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  发过来联系电话和地址\NAll right, send contact numbers and addresses
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.51,0:31:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold Ramsey和Ronald Underwood两个人的\NFor both harold ramsey and ronald underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.78,0:31:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,发送  已发送\NSent and sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.21,0:31:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.37,0:31:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  是Harold Ramsey么\NYes, is this harold ramsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.07,0:31:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NYes, speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.01,0:31:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  Ramsey先生  我是社会保障署的Alex Blake\NHello, mr. Ramsey. This is ssa alex blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.84,0:31:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我和FBI探员在一起\NI'm with the fbi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI\NFbi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.12,0:31:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramsey先生\NMr. Ramsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.72,0:31:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.98,0:31:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramsey先生\NMr. Ramsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.01,0:32:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样\NHow does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.98,0:32:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么干\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.51,0:32:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在是希望他们都来这儿看到此景\NI just wish they were all here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.78,0:32:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.02,0:32:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该握握手然后忘掉这事\NMaybe we should shake hands and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.18,0:32:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你想说的  对么\NThat's what you'd say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.19,0:32:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Riley\NRiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.44,0:32:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,回班吧  你也是\NGet to class. You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.31,0:32:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,各回各班\NEverybody back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.51,0:32:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,表演结束了\NShow's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.12,0:32:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们都对我们做了什么\NYou knew what they did to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.49,0:33:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却无动于衷\NAnd you did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我和他们握手言和\NAnd you wanted me to shake their hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.17,0:33:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们握手言和\NShake their hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.14,0:33:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的以为那样就能解决任何事\NDid you actually think that would solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.04,0:33:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相信Underwood拥有\NWe believe underwood is in possession
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一把被盗的警用Glock19枪\NOf a stolen police issue glock 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.74,0:33:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们分成3组\NWe'll split up into 3 groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.35,0:33:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要逐个房间排查\NWe'll go room to room,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.10,0:33:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们回到主过道会面\Nand we'll all meet back in the main hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们回到了Underwood开始所有事的地方\NBecause we're back where it all started with underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.65,0:33:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这儿也可能会是他的游戏终点\NThis is likely his endgame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.32,0:33:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说难以预料他何时会\NWhich means there's no telling how far
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.95,0:33:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,结束一切  所以诸位请保重\NHe'll go to play this thing out, so be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.20,0:33:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NUhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.36,0:33:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.70,0:33:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你走\NI said go!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.37,0:33:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ronald  求你了\NRonald, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.80,0:33:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很惊讶你记得我的名字\NI'm surprised you remember my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.87,0:33:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,停手吧\NJust stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.27,0:33:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奥\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.08,0:33:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.21,0:33:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\NGet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.17,0:34:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,动啊\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.54,0:34:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ronald Underwood  FBI  放下武器\NRonald underwood, fbi. Drop the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.07,0:34:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放他走吧  Ronald\NLet him go, ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.74,0:34:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须得知道这种感觉如何\NHe has to know how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.54,0:34:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉他知道了\NI think he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.18,0:34:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他\NLook at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.61,0:34:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放他走吧\NLet him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.35,0:34:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他本应该阻止的\NHe should have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.92,0:34:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你作这事儿的缘由  Ronald\NI know why you're doing this, ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.45,0:34:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,发生在Riley身上的事并不是你的错\NWhat happened to riley wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.43,0:34:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没人阻止\NNobody stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.86,0:34:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人做任何努力\NNobody did anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.60,0:34:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经做了\NYou did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.56,0:34:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你说对了\NYou're damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.93,0:34:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应得的\NAnd they got what they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.53,0:34:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但没人有必要丢命\NBut nobody else needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.50,0:34:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你得放下过去\NYou've got to leave the past in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.88,0:35:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我唯一的朋友\NHe was the only friend I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.85,0:35:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是\NI know he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.88,0:35:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但到此为止了  Ronald\NBut it's all over now, ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.50,0:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计  没事儿  你没必要给我戴手铐\NHey, man, it's ok, you don't have to cuff me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.70,0:35:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了不用拷着我\NI said you don't have to cuff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.27,0:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\NGet off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我说放开\NI said get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.97,0:35:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太紧了  放了我\NThey're too tight! Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.07,0:35:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我说放开\NI said get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.21,0:35:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,放开\NI said get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.14,0:35:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,停下  让我走\NStop! Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.81,0:35:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  放了我吧\NCome on. Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.49,0:35:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊怎么样\NHow's the wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,阵痛啊\NThrobbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.86,0:35:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都还好吗？\NYou all good?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jefferson是我高中时的对手\NJefferson was my rival high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.53,0:36:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那些日子弄个球  来点儿足球赛\NGot dragged to a few football games here back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.07,0:36:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会牵动回忆\NIt must bring back some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.64,0:36:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.74,0:36:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不好的记忆\NBad ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.21,0:36:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你兄弟怎么样了？\NHow's your brother doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.21,0:36:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,脑震荡\NConcussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.48,0:36:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但他醒了\NBut he's awake and...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.42,0:36:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他会没事的\NHe's gonna do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.35,0:36:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\NThank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.95,0:36:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.96,0:36:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想在这儿转转吗\NDo you want a ride over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.16,0:36:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 我妈妈就是在这家医院去世的\NNah. It's the hospital where my mom died
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.47,0:36:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,danny也是\NAnd my big brother danny, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.43,0:36:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.37,0:36:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很想回来这里\NNot exactly raring to get back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.29,0:36:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,头疼好点没？\NHow's the headache?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.23,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,靠药好点\NWell, the medicine's helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:37:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你很幸运\NYou got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.87,0:37:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有后援你不该去的\NYou shouldn't have gone in without backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.23,0:37:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讽刺的是  你的铁头救了你\NIronic that your hard head is what saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.47,0:37:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你真吓着我了\NYou really scared me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.04,0:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,恭贺该一个接一个来了\NI guess congratulations is in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.21,0:37:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们\NMm-hmm. For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.48,0:37:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一起的\NWe did it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.29,0:37:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以老爸是对的\NSo dad was right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.29,0:37:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌那样\NI hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.43,0:37:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NYeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.16,0:37:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\NListen, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.10,0:37:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NListen, I'm really sorry, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.10,0:37:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是一个混蛋  不值得你这样\NI'm sorry for being an ass. You didn't deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.77,0:37:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.38,0:37:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么你让我如此疯狂\NAnd I don't know why you made me so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.61,0:37:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是你姐姐\NBecause I'm your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.71,0:37:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,平常兄妹都是这样抬扛\NIt's--it's normal for siblings to resent each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.78,0:37:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那算什么？\NOk, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:37:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我的定义？\NWhat, is that your profile of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.82,0:37:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抬扛？\NResent?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.29,0:38:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不想和你争吵  alex\NLook, I don't resent you, alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.13,0:38:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你\NI miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.03,0:38:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定有妙法表示出来\NYou sure have a funny way of showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.47,0:38:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的  danny死后  你就走了\NYou know, after danny died, you just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.71,0:38:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈随后\NAnd then with mom, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.99,0:38:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就像  你走后时光停止\Nlike you just stopped coming around altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.68,0:38:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这会儿的你  我的老姐  你自由了\NIt's like here you are, my big sister, and you just bailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.65,0:38:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能呆这儿  Scott\NI couldn't stay here, scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.78,0:38:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  可你知道吗？相信我  我能做到\NI know. You know what? Trust me, I get it, I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.39,0:38:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有意思的是\NBut the funny thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.65,0:38:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你是厉害的语言学家\NHere you are this hot-shot linguist...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.06,0:38:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以保持沉默\NAnd you can never say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.49,0:38:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你从不打电话  不写信\NYou never call, you never write,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.86,0:38:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不做\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.53,0:38:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  你还好吗\NWhat's wrong? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.43,0:38:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的胳膊  中枪了\NOh, yeah. It's just my arm. I got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.44,0:38:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  看  就是这里\NOk, what? See, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.84,0:38:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,的确如我所说\NThat's exactly what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.41,0:38:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.78,0:38:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 爸爸知道吗\NOh, really? Does dad know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.35,0:38:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不  他为什么要知道\NOf course not. Why would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.89,0:39:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是对的\NBut you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.22,0:39:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.76,0:39:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,保持联系让我感觉很不好\NI'm bad about being in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.53,0:39:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而回家\NAnd coming home,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.63,0:39:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说很困难\NIt's really hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.10,0:39:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到你就想起danny\NI see you and I think of danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\NI see dad and...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.87,0:39:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还有妈妈\NI think of mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.11,0:39:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我正在为此努力\NBut I'll work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.45,0:39:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.55,0:39:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想你\NAnd I miss you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.27,0:39:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哈喽\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.37,0:39:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.17,0:39:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们迟到了\NYou're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.44,0:39:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只是\NLike...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.24,0:39:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟而已\NWhat-- 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.84,0:40:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也是迟到了\NYou're still late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.81,0:40:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,瓜怎样 警察\NHow's the melon? Hey, pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.78,0:40:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  还不错  很好\NIt's, uh, it's all right. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.52,0:40:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩和好了  是吗\NAhh, you two made up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.26,0:40:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  你们小时候就经常这样\NYeah, I figured-- heh heh--been doing that since you were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.12,0:40:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,像猫狗一样打架  但十分钟后就忘了\NFight like cats and dogs, then forget about it 10 minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.50,0:40:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,常常让你们母亲抓狂\NUsed to drive your mother crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.06,0:40:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她再向我发飙\NThen she'd drive me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,警察  你知道她中枪了吗？\NHey, pop, you know she got shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.57,0:40:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\NOh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.34,0:40:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.54,0:40:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我听说了\NYeah, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.61,0:40:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说了？\NYou heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miller先生？\NMr. Miller?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.68,0:40:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再来点冰块\NWe need more ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,自便  怎么了\NHey, what's up? Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.28,0:40:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是Scott  我是Penelope\NYou must be scott. I'm penelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.28,0:40:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.18,0:40:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.72,0:40:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀请的他们\NI invited them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.22,0:40:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.19,0:40:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只是俩个半小时的航程\NIt's only a 2 1/2 hour flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.92,0:40:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当我听说堪萨斯城烧烤  我就飞奔而来了\NWhen I hear kansas city barbecue I come a-runnin',
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相对他们  我是一个素食主义者\NFor the sides and the fixin's. I'm a vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.73,0:40:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思  他们\NWhat do you mean, them?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:41:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都在这儿啊\NOh, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.24,0:41:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界发生碰撞了啊\NMy worlds are colliding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.91,0:41:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸答应了要烤排骨\NAnd your dad promised ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.61,0:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你老爸的烤肉可真不是盖的\NAnd your pops is no joke on this grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.31,0:41:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,全家人聚齐了才能庆祝\NCan't celebrate unless the whole family's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.65,0:41:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没意见\NI can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.55,0:41:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谁需要冰的\NAnd who needs a cold one?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.25,0:41:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我有意见也别介意  干杯\NDon't mind if I do. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.62,0:41:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为了Blake  为Blake干杯\NTo blake. To blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.99,0:41:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一人势单力薄\N"Alone we can do so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.16,0:41:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,众人齐力断金\NTogether we can do so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.13,0:41:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen keller\NHelen keller.
